---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ContactCTA from '../../components/ContactCTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Audible — Jason Ferrara">
  <article class="case-study">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <img src="/images/audible/audible_logo_2C_rgb.png" alt="Audible" class="hero-logo" />
          <h1>Modernizing Audible's Platform Experience</h1>
          <div class="hero-meta">
            <span class="meta-detail">UX Director &mdash; Systems & Information Architecture</span>
            <span class="meta-sep">/</span>
            <span class="meta-detail">2020&ndash;2022</span>
          </div>
          <p>Audible was navigating premium content expansion, executive transition, and platform inconsistency across native surfaces. Discovery, navigation, and UI patterns varied across platforms, and legacy technical debt slowed delivery.</p>
          <p>I led platform-level experience modernization across native mobile, aligning architectural clarity, experimentation strategy, and organizational structure to support scalable growth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-visual">
          <img src="/images/projects/audible-tile.png" alt="Audible app redesign — home experience" class="hero-device-img" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Platform Harmonization & Revenue Impact -->
    <section class="cs-section cs-section-alt container">
      <span class="cs-label">Audible Native Apps</span>
      <h2 class="cs-heading">Platform Harmonization & Revenue Impact</h2>
      <p class="cs-intro">Audible's app home experience was fragmented and visually inconsistent across platforms. Simultaneously, premium originals represented only 10% of listening, creating an opportunity to elevate first-party content visibility.</p>
      <p class="cs-intro cs-intro-secondary">I led the redesign of the App Home Hero as a scalable system rather than a one-off visual refresh &mdash; balancing personalization, premium presentation, and performance impact.</p>

      <div class="impact-grid impact-grid-3col">
        <div class="impact-metric">
          <span class="impact-delta">+13.89%</span>
          <span class="impact-label">Originals Listening</span>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-metric">
          <span class="impact-delta">+2.14%</span>
          <span class="impact-label">Revenue Lift</span>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-metric">
          <span class="impact-delta">+0.64%</span>
          <span class="impact-label">Listening Days</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <span class="cs-sublabel">Focus Areas</span>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>Platform Harmonization Across Native Surfaces</h3>
          <p>Addressed UI/UX inconsistencies between iOS and Android and reduced architectural fragmentation across discovery surfaces. Established scalable navigation and content presentation patterns to support premium growth without increasing cognitive load.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>Experimentation-Led Experience Evolution</h3>
          <p>Structured multivariate testing around App Home Hero treatments to validate business impact before scaling. Balanced personalization, revenue sensitivity, and first-party visibility while protecting third-party relationships.</p>
          <p class="feature-aside">This shifted design from visual execution to revenue-influencing experimentation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>Component Strategy & Technical Debt Reduction</h3>
          <p>Faced with a 22-week build estimate for a fully componentized hero system, I led a simplified experimentation path that reduced implementation to 8 weeks &mdash; accelerating speed to market while validating long-term architectural direction.</p>
          <p class="feature-aside">This enabled iterative learning before committing to full system overhaul.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>Organizational Realignment for Velocity</h3>
          <p>Restructured design within product-aligned scrum teams to reduce siloed waterfall delivery. Partnered with Product and Engineering leadership on collaborative roadmap prioritization, aligning highest-impact initiatives with lowest technical cost.</p>
          <p class="feature-aside">This reduced feature timelines that previously spanned 6&ndash;9 months and strengthened cross-functional accountability.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <ContactCTA />

  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Page Gradient */
  .case-study {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0e6db 0%, #f4f0eb 35%, #eef1f5 65%, #f7f5f2 100%);
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 5rem;
  }

  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-logo {
    height: 84px;
    width: auto;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
  }

  .meta-detail {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .meta-sep {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-copy > p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* Hero Visual */
  .hero-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-device-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  /* Section */
  .cs-section {
    padding-top: 5rem;
    padding-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .cs-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cs-heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .cs-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .cs-intro-secondary {
    margin-top: -2.5rem;
  }

  .cs-section-alt {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .cs-sublabel {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  /* Features Grid */
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .feature p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .feature-aside {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  /* Impact */
  .impact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3.5rem 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .impact-grid-3col {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  }

  .impact-metric {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .impact-delta {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .impact-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 5rem 0 3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .impact-grid {
      gap: 2.5rem 2rem;
    }

    .impact-grid-3col {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
